Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:10.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要去学校了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:15.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,也不可能一直请病假不去呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:16.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,生病了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:18.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,准备这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:22.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用为我这么费心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:24.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是我想这样做而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:30.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你喜欢上我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.02,0:00:33.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不可以想H的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:35.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:40.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我为你做晚饭等你回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.71,0:00:44.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这个家里休息就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.29,0:00:46.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不用特意去做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:50.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 这样才能感觉到我在报答你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:54.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉每次干劲十足想做什么的时候总是给我添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.67,0:00:59.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,微波炉 高压锅 空调都是自己坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:01.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是你用得太粗鲁了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.51,0:01:03.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有那么用力…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:06.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不需要你用力气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.74,0:01:09.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的机器真脆弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.51,0:01:14.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 请你老老实实待着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.04,0:01:15.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:19.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:29.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,正好 打你手机都不接所以就过来看看了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:31.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不许看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:31.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.87,0:01:32.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:40.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没有发烧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.56,0:01:43.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:45.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,别为难大病初愈的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.28,0:01:47.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你和以前一样是装病
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:46.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:49.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没有品味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:51.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:57.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依倒是觉得依人的品味很前卫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:59.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依 不用安慰我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:04.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐再见 下次再来看你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:07.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚才来没多久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:08.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:11.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.68,0:04:16.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐 姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:27.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名你明明不用一起出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:29.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为要去打工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:30.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:33.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:35.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人今天样子很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:38.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不奇怪啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:39.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天早上也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:41.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉你很慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏这方面那么敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:49.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:52.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是对苍乃也不能说的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:54.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:56.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你在隐瞒什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:57.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:05.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有 也不用真名来乱猜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:06.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再说根本就没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:08.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:28.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是适合儿童套餐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:31.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌这种玩笑 听腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:38.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你有没有考虑过接下来怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:40.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:42.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你没考虑过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时先看看情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:47.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,总之你先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:49.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我会吃的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:51.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你看都沾上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:56.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡来了 让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:57.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:00.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,给您拿新的纸巾来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:01.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.53,0:06:04.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,和爸爸一起吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:05.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:08.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 如你所说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:11.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,他总是很晚回来所以吃饭也很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:13.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:16.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,您的工作真是非常忙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:19.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是他自己安排不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:20.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:25.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以对爸爸说这样的话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:29.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,若是不对男人这样说他们是不会懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:31.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:34.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 很抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:37.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是很复杂的一个家庭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:41.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是很复杂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:42.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什么复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:46.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,领养无依无靠的孩子来照顾他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:49.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是你刚刚设定的想象？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:52.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊… 神秘的胡子绅士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:55.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 原来你比较中意年长的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:06:58.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名 加班呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天不加了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:03.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有点事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:06.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 真少见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:07.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:12.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:19.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 这个是新产品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,鳄梨味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:22.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这种拉面怎么能吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:26.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,难得在大减价的时候买来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,被压仓货给诱惑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:31.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我对购物在行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:33.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢苟同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:36.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不是说过不用准备晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:39.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 你回来太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:42.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:44.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,车站前的超市
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.82,0:07:46.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你又跑出去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:49.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只要太阳没出来就不要紧的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:52.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是指这个 会发生像上次那样的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不觉得无聊就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:56.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对心脏不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:58.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是脆弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:01.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今不用你说我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:06.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可是还是担心茉莉你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:08.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,给我好好听别人说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:11.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好难吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:13.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这是肯定的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:17.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:19.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是来送报纸的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:20.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:24.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我说房主马上就回来的 所以就让他过会送来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:25.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你去过了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:28.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,包在我身上 还有他说我可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:30.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我洗涤剂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,说顽固油渍都能洗干净
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:36.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:38.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 我去开门
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:48.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,来了来了 现在就来开门
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要锁上门
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:55.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是要锁门的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:58.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,以前不是都不锁的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:09:02.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对了对了 将来每个人的防范意识非常重要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:04.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,非常可疑…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:06.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是你多想了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:09.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 算了 你还没吃晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:11.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:13.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你在慌张什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:15.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你偏偏今天来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:18.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为最近你的样子很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:19.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:23.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,去了医院后也就马上走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:24.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是 身体不怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:28.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我就更要给你做点热腾腾的饭菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:32.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,现在已经很晚了 真名的家人也会担心你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:35.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,给你做好晚饭后就回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,已经吃过了 刚刚吃好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:40.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,尽是谎话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:42.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:42.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等… 等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:43.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 真名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:49.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这一堆杯面是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:53.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:02.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉在楼上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:04.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:09.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么… 在想明天的天空会不会是蓝天的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:16.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是一段日子没来 你居然全在吃杯面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:18.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的这款很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:22.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,瞎说 正是因为吃了这些所以身体才变坏的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:25.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我就让你吃点好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:27.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微弄弄就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:31.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:32.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,果然你还是很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:36.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是鳄梨拉面的缘故吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:40.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:46.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你准备在那里站多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没… 有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.66,0:10:53.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:56.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:08.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名小姐 水开了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:15.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人的女朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:33.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还总算是混的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:38.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果一直这样继续下去 我也坚持不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:42.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我为什么要那么慌慌张张
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:46.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人真下流
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:47.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,禽兽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:48.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:52.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？ 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:57.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不… 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:03.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让姐姐为这点事担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:06.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:09.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,酱油没有了 砂糖和盐也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:15.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,之前全被我打翻的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,胡椒 醋和沙司都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:20.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这些也都被我打翻了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:23.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,之前都打翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:25.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那你现在去买回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:26.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:31.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 因为我要为依人做美味的土豆炖肉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:33.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没调味品也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这可怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:38.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,超市已经关门了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,车站前有24小时便利店的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:43.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:47.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么快去快回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:49.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等… 等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:54.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉那家伙绝对不要出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:32.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,原以为依人肯定藏了些什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:46.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,晚… 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:47.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:50.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:52.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:14:00.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊 一个礼拜之前你就住这了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:07.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 基本上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:09.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,他都让你做些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:12.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦 聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:15.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我还真是清闲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:17.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,有这样说自己的么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:21.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那你替换衣服怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:24.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上都是依人帮我准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,内衣的话就自己啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:28.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真伤脑筋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:31.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,每天这些都用手洗的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:34.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,全部要手洗的时候你怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:36.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,洗的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:38.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,洗的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:40.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:42.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:43.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,秘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:44.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,秘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:45.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:54.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:57.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没有做过H的事情 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:02.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,他回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:18.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:20.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你能为我解释一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:22.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不… 她是我表妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:24.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:25.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:29.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是的 在我找到公寓之前先这里住几天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:30.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:33.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那你为什么要对我隐瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:35.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:38.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我怕生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:39.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:43.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,和我也是初次见面 不是没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:46.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上我很紧张的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:48.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那我可没看出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:50.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,伤脑筋了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:52.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,伤脑筋的人可是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:55.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你也应该早点和我商量好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:57.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你该说的话么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:58.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:15:59.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:04.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是依人的什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:19.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,要说是什么人的话是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:22.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的没有想过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:25.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在公园在教会不是发生了这个那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:27.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:30.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,到… 到底这个怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:34.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说她饿了很困扰 我就收留她了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:36.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:39.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,弃猫？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:40.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,也算是那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.51,0:16:44.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可以再添一碗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:47.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,土豆炖肉实在太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:56.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:16:59.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,慢待了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.08,0:17:02.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:04.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,合格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:09.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话我就可以把不太可靠的依人交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:10.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不可靠的到底是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:13.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个谁都看上去不怎么可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:16.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,垃圾也收拾不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:18.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是谁在增加垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:19.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,还很色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:20.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一点没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,还经常发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:23.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为最近烦恼的事情增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:24.64,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,不过她看上去不像坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:25.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,废话太多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:26.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是你的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:26.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我说依人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:31.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你就那么不信任我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:33.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:36.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你都不告诉我 我怎么来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:45.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 把她捡回来以后由猫变身成人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:47.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:51.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为了在未来世界改变我的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:53.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:00.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想让姐姐担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:04.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了 就是因为这个所以连我都要隐瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:06.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为真名是大嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:09.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你不让我说我是不会说的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人的姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:18.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,现在住院中 从以前开始身体就比较弱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:19.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:24.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 那我就不追究事情根本由来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:27.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你们有其他原因
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:30.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事我不会对任何人说的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:32.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:35.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照 茉莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:45.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,合格
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:49.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:51.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:53.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,话还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:57.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,难得的两人时间 我怎么可以打扰你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:18:59.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,两人时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:00.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:17.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得是个不可思议的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:19.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说是不可思议呢还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:22.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找茉莉多说点话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:28.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,累了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:41.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:43.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,合格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:46.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话我就可以把不太可靠的依人交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我和她说过尽量不要外出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:54.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,应该马上就回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:57.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么说的那么轻松啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.89,0:20:00.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉小姐她不准备回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:02.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会这样想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:03.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,女人的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:06.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人你太迟钝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:08.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,说去找…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:10.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,应该还没走远吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:19.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:21.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那… 那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:25.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿行李了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:29.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不能总是靠借衣服来生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:33.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 接下来你们要去约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:36.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:39.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你们是恋人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:43.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,恋人 你说谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:44.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我和真名？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.83,0:20:46.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:48.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:51.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人是个寂寞的独身男对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你没资格说我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:58.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,别看我现在这样 有时候也会有人向我告白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:00.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的最近是什么时候的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:03.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小学四年级
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:04.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:08.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 就这样先安心住下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:12.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那我就再住一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:14.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:17.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 我又没怎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:19.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:20.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你这「好了」是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:39.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没见森宫同学迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:40.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:50.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我说为什么只跟真名打招呼啊 可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:55.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你在笑什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.89,0:21:59.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可疑…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.18,0:23:32.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我是苍乃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:33.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我是小依
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.68,0:23:35.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,来段绕口令吧
